# Claude Instructions

Read `AGENTS.md` first. This workspace is managed by devteam and should not be
treated as a single repository.

Before editing code, inspect the dynamic workspace context and bind this
session to a track:

```bash
node "{{DEVTEAM_CLI}}" workspace context --root "$PWD" --for claude --text
node "{{DEVTEAM_CLI}}" track list --root "$PWD" --active-only --text
```

After the user chooses a track:

```bash
node "{{DEVTEAM_CLI}}" track context --root "$PWD" --set "<track>" --text
```

Use session-local track selection such as `--set <track>` or `DEVTEAM_TRACK`
instead of relying on a global active track.

